dct_title_s: Wiltonia, sive, Comitatus Wiltoniensis, anglis Wil Shire [verso]
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Includes 14 coats of arms. Shows hundreds and main roads. Dutch text on verso with caption title: Wiltonia, of, Wilshire; signature Mm2. From: Nieuwen Atlas, ofte werelt-beschrijvinghe ... Amstelodami : Apud Ioannem Ianssonium, 1647.
